title: I Got A Speeding Ticket On A Bicycle… For Jeff Bezos
description: In this video, YouTuber Max Fosh gets a speeding ticket while riding a bicycle in an attempt to prank Jeff Bezos.
summary: Max Fosh pretends to be Jeff Bezos and gets a speeding ticket on a bicycle.
payoff: The humor comes from the absurdity of someone getting a speeding ticket on a bicycle, especially when pretending to be the richest man in the world, Jeff Bezos.
